    "body": "You seem to have installed the gRPC C library in a path that is not in your default include path or link search path. I think that it should work if you prefix the `npm install` command with `CPPFLAGS=-I/usr/local/include LDFLAGS=-L/usr/local/lib` instead of making that edit to `binding.gyp`.\n"
